# Past Cryptocurrency Development Work

Here are some of my past contributions to blockchain ecosystems:

## [Validator Monitoring Tool](https://github.com/yourusername/validator-monitoring)
- Developed an open-source tool for monitoring validator node health, including uptime, missed blocks, and network latency. Integrated with Prometheus and Grafana for real-time insights.

## [Blockchain Node Automation Scripts](https://github.com/yourusername/node-automation-scripts)
- Created a set of automation scripts for easier deployment and maintenance of blockchain nodes using Bash, Ansible, and Terraform.

## [Consensus Algorithm Optimization Research](https://github.com/yourusername/consensus-research)
- Published research on optimizing PoS consensus algorithms to improve finality times and decentralization. Shared with blockchain projects to enhance network performance.

## [Blockchain Documentation Contributions](https://github.com/yourusername/blockchain-docs)
- Contributed detailed, easy-to-understand guides for node setup, staking, and API usage across various blockchain projects.
